Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:11.40,Default,Ooyama,0,0,0,,{富士見学園もこれで立派に誇れるものはできたと言うわけですよ。}Fujimi Academy's success increased the school's prestige.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:12.26,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{え。}I see.
