Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.69,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{あ、本郷先生。}Ah, professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:31.25,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{こちらはね、市会議員、大山さん。}This is mr. Ooyama, a member of the city council.
