Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:02.39,Default,Ooyama,0,0,0,,{かれから何でもご相談くださいよ。}Don't hesitate to ask for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.73,Default,Ooyama,0,0,0,,{できるかぎりの援助させてもらいますから。}I will help you out as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:06.58,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{ありがとうございます。}Thank you very much.
