Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.32,Default,Boy B,0,0,0,,{あ、分かっちゃいないな。}What a lost case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.90,Default,Boy B,0,0,0,,{同じクラスじゃないから言うんだよ。}You tell it {\i1}because{\i0} you're not in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:53.45,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—ささささ！\N—ちょっと待って、おい！}– Come on, come on!\N– Hey, don't push me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.34,Sign,,0,0,0,,{新聞部部室}Newspaper club
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:57.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{努くん。}Tsutomu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.43,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{や、ちょっと待って。}Ah, just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:00.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え、いいわ。}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.81,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{おい、早く行って。こら。}Get going already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.43,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{XXX}Hurry up and be done with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.20,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{ほれ。ほれ。}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:08.23,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{あの。}Err.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.38,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{あ-あ-鮎原さん。}A-A-Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:10.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:12.67,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{今日は。}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:13.58,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{あの…}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:14.73,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{じ-実は、その…}A-Actually, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.32,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{あの…}Uhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:18.51,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{ぼ-僕、いえ、あの…}I-I— nah, err…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:20.70,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{友達はいいですね…その、いや、あの…}Friends are nice… uh, that's not it…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:22.86,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{あの…や、違いました。あの…}I got it wrong. Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:23.77,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{その…}You see…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:29.39,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{あの、なっていただけるなんてことは…ない…ですね。}Looks like… I can't express myself very well… don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:30.61,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{あの…}Err…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.47,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{お、おうき。}Oh. Ooki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.06,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{何だ？}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.73,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{お！一ノ瀬！や、別に。}Ah! Ichinose! It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:39.04,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{どうも失礼しました。さようなら。}Excuse me. Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.57,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{どうしたんだ？}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:46.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{何でもないの。}Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そんなことよりね、努くん。}Never mind that, Tsutomu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{今日パーティに行かない？}Are you going to today's party?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:55.43,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{パーティ？}Party?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:58.10,Default,Boy B,0,0,0,,{へ。だらし無いな。}Heh. How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.75,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{だってお前も見ただろ。一ノ瀬が来ちゃったんだろ。}Well, you saw it, didn't you? Ichinose came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:01.86,Default,Boy C,0,0,0,,{不味いよ。}It was a bad timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.41,Default,Boy A,0,0,0,,{一ノ瀬じゃ不味いな。}Ichinose is what's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.33,Default,Boy A,0,0,0,,{あいつには敵わない。}You don't stand a chance with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:10.36,Default,Boy B,0,0,0,,{え、俺たちじゃ相手にならんもんね。え、がっくり。}Eh, we can't ever land a girl. What a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.83,Default,Boy A,0,0,0,,{あ、若いって悩み多いな。切ないこと。}Youth has lots of problems. It's painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.60,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{市の祝賀パーティが？}The city's throwing a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そう。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{大変よ、球に人気ものになっちゃって。}Being suddenly famous is no easy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.27,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{今朝もね、一年生にサインも頼まれたのよ。}Just this morning some girls asked me for an autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.12,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{サイン？}Autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.34,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{サインか？へ？}Autograph, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ね、一緒に行かない？}Hey, why don't we go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:31.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしたちも今日は練習を早く切り上げたんだから。ね？}Our practice was cut short today. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.12,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{練習を切り上げた？}The practice was cut short?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:35.68,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{パーティのために？}For some party?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:36.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうよ。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:39.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それにここんとこあたしたちはちょっと疲れてるし。}Besides we're a bit tired lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:42.13,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{そう？残念だけど、編集会議に伸ばせないから。}Is that so? Too bad, I have to attend an editorial meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ん？じゃ、仕方は無いわね。}It can't be helped then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:44.70,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{よい。}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あ、泉水さんだわ。}Ah, it's Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうだ。泉水さん誘っちゃう。}All right, I'll invite Izumi-san instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.84,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—泉さぁぁ—\N—止せよ。}– Izumi-sa—\N– Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:52.62,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え-え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.58,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{泉水くんは懸命に練習してるんだよ。}Izumi-san giving her all in the practice…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.32,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{君は有頂天なってるけど。}…while you're walking on air.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:08:00.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あら？あたしは別に有頂天になんか。}Oh? I'm not walking on air.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.82,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{何だかそんなに気がするんだよ。}You're giving off that vibe, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:04.08,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{有償して皆にスターXXされて…}People treat champions like stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.04,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{…それでいい気になっているような。}Looks like it makes you feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{嫌な言い方ね。そう言う努くんのほうこそ。}You're unkind. Besides, Tsutomu-kun, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:12.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{スポーツをやらないあなたの僻み見たに聞こえるわよ。}You act like you know it all, while in reality you never did any sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.16,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{な-何だって？}Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうでしょう？あたしたちは優勝したのよ。}Am I not right? At any rate, we won the championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:19.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{サーツXXされたとしてもいいじゃないの？}What's wrong with being treated like stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:19.66,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:22.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{君は…}Why…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:27.10,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{君は一体なんのためにバレーをやってるんだ？}What the heck are you playing volleyball for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:31.52,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{大会に優勝してカップや優勝旗を飾り優越感に浸るためだったのか？}Was it to win contests, get capes and pennants and bask in the glory?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.34,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{優勝してなにが悪いのよ？}What's wrong with winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:36.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{スポーツは優勝するためにこそあるのよ。}Sports exist precisely so that people can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:37.57,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{き-君は…}Y-You're—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.07,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{一ノ瀬さん！}Ichinose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.84,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{一ノ瀬さん、どうしたの？}Ichinose-san, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.25,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{いや、何でもない。}An, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.69,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{あ、招待しておくよ。}Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.92,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{三年二組ののざわゆきこくん。}She's Nozawa Yukiko-kun, a third-year from class 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.52,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{バレー部の鮎原さんね。}You're Ayuhara-san of the volleyball club, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:54.86,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{有償お目出度う。}Congratulations on winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.63,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{あなたの活躍はとても素晴らしかったわ。}Your success was very wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:58.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{どうも。}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.38,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{あたしは新聞部ののざわゆきこです。}I'm Nozawa Yukiko of the newspaper club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.05,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{よろしくね。}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:04.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{よろしく。}My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:05.37,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{あ、そうだ。}Ah, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:10.19,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{編集会議の前に君はこのXXこと、整理しとかなきゃいけなかったな。}You wanted to sort out the notes before the editorial meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.54,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{それじゃ、失礼するよ。}Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.63,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{それじゃ、これからも頑張ってな、鮎原さん。}Please keep doing your best, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.53,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{あ、ちょっと、一ノ瀬さん！}Hold on, Ichinose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.76,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしが優勝していい気に成ってるなんて…}I bask in the glory after winning the championship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:37.25,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そんな…そんなこと絶対にないわ。}That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:40.49,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{一、二。一、二。}One. Two. One. Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:41.25,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{ほら。}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:43.21,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{XXX}Keep at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.89,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{もっとXXX。}Let's see more vigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:45.68,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{ほら、どうした？}What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.60,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{ほら、元気出せ。}Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.44,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{ほれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:50.83,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:52.72,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{っせ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:57.50,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{こずえさん！}Kozue-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.31,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{こずえさん、なにぐずぐずしてるの？}Kozue-san, why are you spacing out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:03.40,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{早く帰ってXXないとパーティに遅れるわよ。}We need to hurry up and change, or we'll be late to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.72,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{あ、泉水さんたちも誘うわね。}Ah, let's invite Izumi-san and the girls too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:06.91,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ダメなんだって。}They won't be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:07.92,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{どうして？}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:13.14,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{あ。ね、どんな服着ていく？}Say, what are you going to wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.48,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{XXXたくさんXXでしょう？}There will be lots of city people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:17.01,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{どんな服がいいかな？}What would be good, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.82,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{ん、あんまりXXX}It can't be too flashy, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.80,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{あたし何着ていかなっちゃうわ。}I can't really decide what to put on…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:22.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ん。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:43.22,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,0)}{富士見学園女子バレーボール部全日本選手権大会優勝祝賀会会場}Fujimi Academy girls volleyball club All-Japan championships celebration venue
Comment: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:50.07,Sign,,0,0,0,,{祝・富士見学園\N女子バレーボール部\N全日本選手権大会優勝\N祝賀会}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:57.48,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{では、本日の会話を祝しまして私から一言お祝いを申し上げます。}Well then, I'd like to say a word before we open the celebration party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:11:01.87,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{この旅の富士見学園女子バレーボール部の優賞は…}The victory the Fujimi Academy's volleyball club girls have seized…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:06.91,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{単に、富士見学園に輝かしき栄光をもたらしたばかりではなく。}…doesn't bring glory only to the Fujimi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:10.68,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{わが富士見ヶ浜XXXを一躍日本中に広め}It also promotes our Fujimigahama city across the whole Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:14.33,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{市の発展に大いなる貢献をしたと言えましょう。}It can be said they made a great contribution to the city development.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:19.40,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{今回富士見学園女子バレーボール部が成し遂げた第XXXは。}Seeing how much Fujimi Academy's volleyball club girls have accomplished…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:25.79,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{いかほどに賞賛いたしましても、賞賛しすぎるということはないのであります。}…no matter how much one praises them, one can't praise too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.06,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうよ。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:39.42,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{私たちは自分の力でこの栄光をつかんだのよ。}We achieved this glory with our own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:57.07,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{さ、行くわよ。}All right, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:58.75,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.17,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{あ…あぁ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:03.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい。次！}Okay. Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:04.60,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:07.69,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{さ、次！}Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:11.35,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{うまくXXあたし？XXX}– I wonder if I can pass it?\N– I'm anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:13.77,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.12,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{いやだ。}Ah, damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:15.96,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{あらあら。}Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:24.83,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{ね、バレー部に入りたい人が沢山いるとは聞いただけど、こんなに沢山は集まるとはね…}I heard there will be lots of people wanting to join our club, but I never imagined this many.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:27.24,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{当然。日本一のバレー部だもん。}It's only natural. We're the best in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:30.01,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{でも、大変よ。こんな部下を選ぶのは。}But this selection is a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.88,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{仕方ないわね、それぐらいわ。}It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:33.68,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{ま、有名税てとこね。}It's the price for our fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:34.82,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{エヘヘ。}Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:42.81,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{はい、二、二、三、三二三。}Okay, two-two-three, three-two-three.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:44.64,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{はい、思いっきりおく。}Put all your heart into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.86,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{そう。}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:46.89,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{そう。いいわよ。}Good. It's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.60,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{中島先生。どうもすみません。}Sorry for the bother, professor Nakajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.41,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{いつまでも体育館を使ってしまって。}We're using the gym again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.87,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{いいえ。}Ah, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.60,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{今日は体操部の練習があったのに、どうも。}But today is gymnastics club's practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:13:00.08,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{同じ運動部として、よろこんで強力しますわ。}We're in the same sports section. I'll gladly cooperate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:01.63,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{いかがですか？テストの方は。}How is the selection going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.29,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{中々大変です。}It's quite a chore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:04.91,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{でも素晴らしいことですわ。}But it's a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:05.86,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{や…}I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.12,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{あら、何か？}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:08.52,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{お祭りさい見たいなもんです。}It feels like school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:09.33,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{え？}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:13.30,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{選手達も一緒に成って、いつまでも浮ついた気分でなきゃいいんだ。}I'd rather the students stayed more focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:15.87,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{しばらくわ。仕方ないかもしれませんわね。}Be patient. There's not much we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:20.54,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{僕もなるべくならうるさい事と言って(XXX・押さえ)つけたくありません。}I don't want to be too much of a nag to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.77,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{皆をもっと大きく(XX・育てたい)ですからね。}But I also want to raise them as well as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.36,Sign,,0,0,0,,{バレー部々室}Volleyball club's room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:27.53,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{ああ。やっと終わったわね。}Ah, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{本当ね。}Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:33.26,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{なんだか練習の時に疲れちゃったみたいだわ。}I'm tired like after practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:38.72,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{え、新入部員を迎えて、我が富士見学園女子バレー部員は…}By welcoming the new club members, our Fujimi Academy's volleyball club…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:42.01,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{…また一段と大きな飛躍を遂げるやりましょう。}…manages to struggle through yet another crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.32,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{ハハハハ。}Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:45.88,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{ね、キャプテン。}Hey, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:49.64,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{新しい部員は入ってきたらこの部屋で狭いじゃないかしらね。}With all the new members this room will get cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうね。}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.89,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{それに練習時間こともあるわ。}Besides, there's the issue of practice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:57.29,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{今まであたしたちの練習だけでも十分に時間を取れなかったのよ。}There wasn't enough time even just for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.92,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{そうよね。}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.44,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{そうね。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:03.92,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{体操部や卓球部交代で体育館を使ってるんですもんね。}We have to use the gym in turns with the table tennis and gymnastics clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:04.67,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{ん、んん。}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:10.10,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{折角新しい部員達は入ってきても、練習時間がないような状態では何もならないと思うわ。}Accepting all the new members will be meaningless if we don't even have the time to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:13.66,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—そうよね。\N—ね、キャプテン。なんとかしなくちゃ。}– Yeah.\N– Captain, we need to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.45,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{ね、キャプテン。おねがいします。}Captain, we're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.22,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{大きくなって、われわれバレー部のために。}All for our newly expanded club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.97,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—お願いします。—お願いします。\N—え。}– We're counting on you.\N– Please.
Comment: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:23.33,Sign,,0,0,0,,{表賞状／ 優賞／ 東海地区代表／ 富士見学園バレー部／ 全国中学校女子バレーボールXX／ 大会にXいて、頭Xの成XをXめましたのX、／ Xにいての学XをXXXXいれします。／ 昭和四十四年五月十日／ 全国中学校バレーボール協会／ 全長 三X X}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:27.97,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{それは皆の意見なのか？}Is that everyone's conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:32.25,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{新しい部員室のことは校長や教頭とも相談してみよう。}Let's ask the principal and the\hvice-principal about a new club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:33.69,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{何とか成るだろう。}Who knows what they will say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:37.12,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{しかし、鮎原。体育館での練習時間のほうだが…}However, Ayuhara, what about the gym practices?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:42.06,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{君が今言っただけどうしても必要となると体操部や卓球部は一体どうなる？}You say you need it no matter what, but what about the table tennis and the gymnastics clubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それは…}That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.33,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{どうするんだ、鮎原?}What will we do, Ayuhara?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それは…仕方はありません。}That's… that can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:49.39,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{ん？}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:55.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{体操部や卓球部の練習時間が少なくなったとしても、それは仕方はありません。}Even if the table tennis and gymnastics clubs' practice time gets cut, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:58.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{バレー部は全日選手権本大会に優勝しました。}Our volleyball club has won in the All-Japan championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:15:01.48,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そしてこれからXX伝統を是非守っていきたいと思います。}We also want to protect our title in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:04.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それで他の部はどうなってもいいと言ってありませんが…}I don't want to say I don't care what happens to the other clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:08.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{…そのために多少の迷惑がかかってもそれは仕方ないと思います。}But even if we cause some inconvenience, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.93,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{仕方はないか。}Can't be helped, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.39,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{よし。分かった。}I see. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:21.86,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{本郷くんから話のあった。バレー部のことなんだがね。}Professor Hongou wants to talk about the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:25.63,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{新しい部員室を作ることはクラブ会費の残額で十分です。}Creating a new club room should fit in the club budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.36,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{そう。それはよかった。}I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:31.58,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{学園としてもバレー部に力を入れていくべきでそれぐらいは当然でしょ。}Even as an academic institution, it's natural to emphasize the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:36.41,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{また部員室の事ばかりでなく今後も必要経費が出てくるでしょうから…}Since the expenses will come out not only in the new club room, but also in the future…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:40.33,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{このさいクラブの予算を検討し直してはと思いますが。}…I think that I will review this club's budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:46.58,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{ん。しかし検討し直すと言っても予算を増やすわけにはいかんだろう。}Hm. However, it might turn out it's not possible to increase the budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:50.20,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{それは市から援助金が出ることになってはいるんだね。}We're supposed to receive grant money from the city, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:54.84,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{いいぇ、援助金はいざという時にして現行の予算を組み替えるということです。}The aid money is to be used only in an emergency case where we deplete our current budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:56.97,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{もちろん、バレー部を重点的にして。}Of course, with the focus on the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:16:00.93,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{それからこの際クラブそのものも検討する必要があるんでは。}Because of this, we might be forced to examine the clubs themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:02.35,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{んん。}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:11.92,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{危ない！}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.26,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{大丈夫？}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:14.26,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{大丈夫です。}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.98,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{ちょっとXXXだけです。}I only slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:19.02,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{外で練習なんかしてると今に本当に怪我しちゃうわ。}We're getting really hurt now that we practice outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:22.89,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{—体育館でできないなら、練習なんかやめちゃうといるよ。\N—そうよ。}If we can't do it in the gym, we shouldn't practice at all in my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:25.20,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{体育館を日本一のバレー部成員X出す。}She gave our gym to the Japan's best volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.29,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{中島先生は本郷先生に弱しね。}Prof. Nakajima has a weak spot for prof. Hongou, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.97,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{皆、どうしたの？}What is it, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:29.54,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{え？}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:31.96,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{どうしたの？言ってごらんなさい。}Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:36.66,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{皆で…体操部は体育館で練習すべきだっと話したんです。}We were talking about how the gymnastics club should practice in a gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:37.37,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{ね？}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:40.41,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{体育館でも練習してるじゃないの。}We're practicing at the gym too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:43.05,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{足りない時間を外でしてるだけでしょう。}We're only doing it outdoors when we're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.63,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{今までは全部体育館でできました。}Until now, we were practicing inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.40,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{え。確かに。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:50.00,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{でも、それはバレー部の練習時間は多くなったからでしょう。}But volleyball club's practice time was lengthened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:54.97,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{バレー部が全日本で優勝したから、仕方がないですか、中島先生？}Are you saying that because they're the Japan's best, it can't be helped, prof. Nakajima?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:57.63,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{だれもそんなことは言っていません。}No one says such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.22,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{バレー部はね、部員の数が増えたでしょう。}They got many freshmen recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:02.84,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{それだけ練習の時間が増えるのは当然です。}It's only natural to lengthen their practice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:04.55,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{そうでしょ？}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:12.34,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{体育館でしか練習できない人は外での練習はやめてもいいのよ。}Those who can only practice in the gym can stop coming to the practices outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:15.03,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{スポーツはやれる人だけがやればいいの。}Sports should be done only by people capable of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:15.95,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{はい。次。}All right. Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:20.83,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{よし。}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:21.78,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{はい。次。}Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:30.23,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{いい？こう言う風に手をあわせて。}See? You join your hands like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:31.24,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{何ですか？}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.92,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{僕は卓球部の高橋です。}I'm Takahashi of the table tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:40.48,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{あの、実は練習時間のことだけど。}I came here to ask you about the practice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:44.80,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{今度決められた練習時間では部員の皆がちょっと足りないんじゃないかって言うんで。}The new practice times are a little short for our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:45.78,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{それで…}Because of that…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:47.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そう言われても困るわ。}I don't know what to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:53.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは本郷先生に相談して、職員会議の結果決められたことだし。}We asked professor Hongou and it was decided as a result of the staff meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:55.84,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{それは分かっているんだけど。}I understand it well, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.33,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{皆が…}I can't speak for the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:01.29,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{ちょっと。練習は外でもできるでしょう？}Hey, you can practice outdoors, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:03.29,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{体操部だって外でやってるじゃない？}Even the gymnastics club can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:08.30,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{じゃ、バレー部以外は外で結構だと言うの？}In that case, the same goes to your volleyball club, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.39,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{あら。XXXね？}Oh? An attack already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:12.71,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{優勝したからって威張れないでよ。}Don't get cocky just because you're champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.34,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{何も威張ってないわ。}Nobody's getting cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:18.31,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{でも優勝したって言うのはそれだけ実力なると言うことね。}But us being champions is just a sign of our skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:20.38,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{あたしたちにはコーチも先生もいないわ。}We don't even have a coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.17,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{それに部員の数も少ないわ。}We're lacking club members, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:24.29,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{だからと言って、バカにしないでよ。}Don't take us lightly just because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.33,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{小林さん。}Kobayashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.03,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{いいの。}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:32.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{今のバレー部にはどうしてもこれだけの練習時間は必要なの。}We absolutely need that much of the practice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.43,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{フン。何よ！}Hmph. We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:35.80,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{どうもすみません。}Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:40.58,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{言うだけ言ってXXXきたのね。僻みっぽい練習。}They only came to make us nervous. What a jealous bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.99,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{ま。さて、練習、練習。}All right, practice, practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:50.90,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{鮎原。どうかしたのか？}Ayuhara. Something's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:51.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？いいえ。}Eh? Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:55.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{先生、実は…}Professor, actually…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.54,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{明日東京のバレーボール協会行ってくる。}I'm going to Tokyo Volleyball Association tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:00.60,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{二、三(時・日)掛かるかもしれない。}I should be back in two-three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.27,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{バレーボール協会？}Volleyball Association?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{何ですか？}Why are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:07.21,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{試合のスケジュールのことや何かについてちょっと打ち合わせがあるんだ。}To discuss about your game schedule and some other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{どこかと試合するんですか？}Who are we playing against next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.47,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{ん、未だ具体的に決まったわけじゃない。}It's not fully decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:13.35,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{さ、練習だ。}Come on. Practice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:13.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.30,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{あら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:16.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:17.34,Default,Ikezaki,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:18.88,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.25,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{さ、行くわよ。}Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:20.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.86,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{卓球部は廃部に成ったそうだよ、鮎原くん。}Looks like the table tennis club gets disbanded, Ayuhara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:26.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{へ？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:30.43,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{部員の数は少ないし、対校試合にも全く成績が振るわないのが。その原因らしい。}The cause seems to be the low member count and their poor results in the contests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:31.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そう？}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:33.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それで？}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:38.59,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{それでって…君の意見を聞きたいと思ってね。}"So?" I came here to get your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:45.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{意見なんてないわ。}I don't have anything to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.43,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{本当にないのか？}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{何だって言うの？}What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:50.65,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{卓球がバレー部の犠牲になったとでも言うの？}That the table tennis club fell victim to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:51.77,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{そんなこと言ってるんじゃないの。}I don't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そ。それならいいけど。}Hm. Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:54.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{じゃ。}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:56.94,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{き-君は…！}H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:20:00.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{もし犠牲になったのだとしても、それはそれで仕方ないことね。}Even if they fell victim to us, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:06.88,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{もう一度行こう。}Let's do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:07.78,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{よい！}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:09.39,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{はい！}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:18.53,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{へ。}Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:19.44,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{よし、よし。}Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.39,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{もう一息だ。}One more lapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.94,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{大会には絶対新記録を出すんだ。}We'll aim for a new contest record.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:24.97,Default,Kajioka,0,0,0,,{いいな？バレー部に負けるな。}Got it? Don't lose to the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:34.57,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい、いくぞ。}Okay, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:36.03,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{よし、いいぞ。こっち回せ。}Good going. Pass it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:37.03,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{どうした？}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:38.09,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:40.20,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{さ、行くぞ！}Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:42.56,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{それ！シュート！}Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:45.28,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{バカやろ！}Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:47.17,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{そんなこと試合に勝ってると思ってのか？}Think we can win in the game like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:49.23,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{負けてみろ。卓球部見たいに成っちまいぞ。}Lose and you'll be like the table tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:52.14,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{勝つんだ。試合にどんなことあっても、勝つんだ。}We need to win. Real games are all about winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:52.82,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい。}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:01.04,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{バレー部の優勝が刺激になってるのは良いけど…}It's nice that our victory has given people a motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:03.18,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{卓球部は無くなってしまうなんて。}But for the table tennis club to get disbanded?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:04.76,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:05.89,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{どうかしたの？}Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:07.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あ。中島先生。}Ah, professor Nakajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:09.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{いえ。別に何でもありません。}Everything is fine. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:09.81,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{そう。}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:14.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あの、本郷先生未だ帰ったら知らないでしょうか？}Do you not know if professor Hongou is back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:16.06,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{え。未だよ。}He's still out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:17.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうですか。}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:18.46,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:21.18,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{あなた…何が考えることがあるのね？}You're thinking of something, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:25.38,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{あなたの考えてる通りにすればいいんじゃないの？}Why don't you do as your heart tells you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:30.81,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{本郷先生もあなたの考えることまでコーチできないわ。}Professor Hongou cannot coach your own thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:36.02,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{ゲームが始まってコートに入ったら、キャプテンのあなたは判断して、皆を指示するんでしょう？}When the game starts and you enter the court, you, the captain, is the judge. You direct everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:37.79,Sign,,0,0,0,,{卓球部}Tennis table club
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:50.41,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{こずえくん。}Kozue-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:54.53,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{君に見せたいものがあるんだ。}I want to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.53,0:21:55.48,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{一緒に来てくれ。}Please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:00.60,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{ここだよ。}This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:01.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{へ？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.03,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{卓球台が仕舞われたんだよ。}It's the end of the table tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:04.33,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{この物置に。}Right in this cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:06.68,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{我楽多と一緒にね。}Just like a piece of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:11.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ま。}My.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:12.24,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:20.59,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{それ１}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:25.05,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{50。}50.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:25.99,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{51。}51.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:26.93,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{52。}52.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.93,0:22:27.94,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{53。}53.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:28.88,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{54。}54.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:29.92,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{55。}55.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.92,0:22:30.94,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{56。}56.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:32.09,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{57。}57.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.09,0:22:33.15,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{58。}58.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:34.22,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{59。}59.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:35.07,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{60。}60.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:36.22,Default,Kobayashi,0,0,0,,{60…}60…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:43.16,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{高橋はね。部がなくなっても好きなものだけ集まって愛好会としてやっていくそうだ。}Takahashi, even after his club got disbanded, continues to play as it's his favorite activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:47.58,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{一ノ瀬さん。}Ichinose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.67,0:22:51.23,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{あ、のざわくん。なんだ？}Ah, Nozawa-kun. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.23,0:22:52.32,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{あの…}Uhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:54.45,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{いいよ、別に。鮎原くんのいても。}It's okay. You can speak before Ayuhara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:22:57.42,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{運動部の予算のこと。}It's about the sports section budgets.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:23:01.96,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{いくらバレー部にかけたとしても、卓球部は廃部するほどじゃないわ。}No matter how much they spend on the volleyball club, they shouldn't disband the table tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:05.05,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{ここに各クラブの予算書があるんだけど。}Here is the budget for each club.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:06.83,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{高橋のように。}People like Takahashi…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.83,0:23:09.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{本当に好きでやっていこうって言うのが、スポーツじゃないかな。}…just do what they love the most. Isn't it a true sportsmanship?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:12.78,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{それがスポーツの本来姿だと思うわ。}I think it's the essence of the sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:14.47,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{真のスポーツとは何か？}What is considered true sports?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:18.98,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{僕は卓球部の廃部問題に関係させて、新聞に取り上げをと思うんだ。}I think I'll get involved with the table tennis club and cover their story in our newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.05,0:23:23.18,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{ね、あなたも強力してくれない、鮎原さん？}Why don't you help us out, Ayuhara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.18,0:23:26.20,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,{あなたに真のスポーツが分からないはずないわよね。}There's no way you wouldn't know sports true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:30.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{スポーツは理屈じゃないわ。}Sports is not a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.25,0:23:33.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あなたたちにはスポーツなんて分かりXわ。}You don't understand sports at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.23,0:23:57.65,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{本郷コーチは来日中のソ連チームとの練習試合を発表した後…}Coach Hongou, after announcing a practice game with the Soviet team…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:24:00.96,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{「何のためにバレーをやるのか？」XXXの質問をはなった。}…challenges the club with the question: "why are you playing?".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:04.04,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{そして、「それが分かるまで、コーチを下りる」と言う。}"I won't coach you until you're able to answer this question."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:07.56,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{一方バレー部は十分な練習ができないと学校に対し…}Meanwhile, the club, unable to hold enough practice…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:09.45,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{…専用体育館を要求した。}…asks the school for a dedicated gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.45,0:24:13.17,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{努はそんなバレー部を学園新聞で激しく批判した。}Tsutomu strongly criticizes the club's actions in the school newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.17,0:24:17.85,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{こずえはいかりサッカー部の三田村はこずえに味方し努を殴りつけた。}Kozue finds an ally in Mitamura of the football club, who hits Tsutomu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.85,0:24:21.35,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
